data.description: Nestled in the vibrant heart of Manassas, this captivating home offers an ideal blend of comfort and convenience. Spread across three levels, including a finished basement, this residence invites you to make it your own. Upstairs, discover four tranquil bedrooms and two full baths, while downstairs features a versatile den tailored to your needs and an additional full bath with backyard access in the basement. Meticulously cared for with love and attention, this home awaits its next fortunate owners
